{"tid":1499640,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"請問有冇師兄知呢啲係咩嚟？","createTime":"2019-08-23T19:15:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T02:36:42.000Z","uid":133289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4c2060b1a1e79cee93fb1431591bb299941528c2","tid":1499640,"uid":133289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:15:26.000Z","msg":"頭先攞車，發覺好似有啲隨時白色油漆嘅嘢，初頭以為雀屎嚟，但後尾抹完就變咗咁，用手指刮唔係好刮得甩，仲要有啲吱吱聲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n應該唔係油漆，因為以前中過油漆係抹唔甩的<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有冇師兄解答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同埋應該點清理？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：泊村屋閘內，計埋地下得三層，天台應該唔會有嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wjpSNme.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwjpSNme.png&h=e36fdcd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Adknp71.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAdknp71.png&h=94c314d1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"644bee2eab4ce9318886f17708c959941ae71aa0","tid":1499640,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:34:08.000Z","msg":"好似係刮痕喎"},{"pid":"cdfe8268290fb80e9b182f34c8de7fddba005ff3","tid":1499640,"uid":133289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"644bee2eab4ce9318886f17708c959941ae71aa0","tid":1499640,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:34:08.000Z","msg":"好似係刮痕喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:58:41.000Z","msg":"師兄，我有試過用力用指甲摑甩佢"},{"pid":"f4131e3136217be0c04dd550038f57636a407738","tid":1499640,"uid":12850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:36:42.000Z","msg":"打蠟應該打得走"}]}